docs.text: Lab Management Getting started Clone it from github git clone git@github.com:ETH-NEXUS/lab_management.git Create the .env file cd lab_management cp .env.TEMPLATE .env vi .env → Replace all the <> . Run it make up Import a compound library In the api container run: ./manage.py import sdf -i /data/S230470.sdf -m /data/S230470_mapping.yml -r 16 -c 24
